UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'An essay about the impact of social media on the modern world is expected to be structured logically. This ensures that the reader can follow the arguments and ideas presented in the essay. There are several ways to ensure that an essay is well-structured. For example, one technique is to use transition words to connect ideas and paragraphs. Transition words help the reader to understand the relationship between the different parts of the essay. However,  it is important to make sure that the transition words used are appropriate for the specific context and that they are used correctly.',
